photo_id

public JSONObject photo_id(java.lang.String id,
                           int image_size,
                           boolean comments,
                           int comment_page,
                           boolean tags)
500px GET_photos_id. Returns detailed information of a single photo in full photo format. Will return additional fields if photoInterface is constructed with valid access token.

Parameters:
id - id of data of photo to return.
image_size - Should be 1 to 4 while 1 being smallest.
comment - set to true to include comments of the photo in response. Comments are returned in order of creation, 20 entries per page.
comment_page - return the specified page from the comments listing. Page numbers are 1-based.
tags - returns an array of tags for the photo.
items - additional parameter for GET_photos_id request. Follow 500px github for more details.
Returns:
JSON response
